{"tid":1062701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔新娘潭路男子車內燒炭身亡","createTime":"2019-03-15T09:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T09:34:22.000Z","uid":60281,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72af3312746caa0cdb0a182a9b6a045f2f22f0b3","tid":1062701,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:08:35.000Z","msg":"又一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大埔新娘潭路燒烤場的停車場，今午（15日）3時許，有漁護署職員途經時，赫見一名男子倒臥在車內毫無反應，心感不妙遂報警求助。警方及救護員趕至將事主救出，經檢驗後證實他已氣絕身亡。由於車內有一盤燒過的炭，不排除事主燒炭輕生，警方封鎖現場，正追查事主身份及死亡原因。 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n利民會： 3512 2626 <br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=c223a37a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190315/photo/bkn-20190315162125649-0315_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190315170534\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190315%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190315162125649-0315_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190315170534&h=bf536fdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190315/mobile/bkn-20190315162125649-0315_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190315%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190315162125649-0315_00822_001.html&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=b772d47b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190315/mobile/bkn-20190315162125649-0315_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9d164f11